*Dinobot looked away from Tavatron, she was searching for something in him 
but there was nothing there to find...but a warrior. He looked back at the 
Ark and growled softly...*

" Perhaps."

* The way that Tavatron looked at him was unnerving, she was trying to find 
something more then a warrior in him but there was nothing more to find. 
Dinobot looked at the Ark but was lost in thoughts, he was a warrior and 
that was all. There was no secret life, no bots that cared for him and no 
bots that he cared for, no excitement, nothing...but a warrior.
One who fought and protected...one who devoted his life to fight a war that 
seemed to have no end.
It may seem sad in a way but that was what he was, a soldier.
Perhaps... one day he would find that he was something more?
One day.*
